description: Stunning 3-Bedroom, 3-Bath Duplex in the Heart of Thomas Park, South Boston! Step into this beautifully designed home where style meets comfort. With soaring 10-foot ceilings, the grand foyer welcomes you into a thoughtfully curated space filled with high-end finishes and modern charm. The chef-inspired kitchen features a 48" stove, stylish accent ceiling, pendant lighting, open shelving, gas cooking, and access to a private elevated deck—perfect for morning coffee or evening gatherings. The sun-filled living and dining area offers seamless flow, ideal for entertaining guests or relaxing at home. Retreat to the luxurious primary suite, complete with a spa-like en-suite bath, double vanities, a glass-enclosed shower, and a generous 4x5 walk-in closet. Enjoy summer evenings on one of two private decks, or take a leisurely stroll through nearby Thomas Park and along the scenic Harbor Walk. This home is your city sanctuary—sophisticated, serene, and ready for its next chapter.
